========================================================================

tmx is a simple library which reads and writes the Tiled TMX format.


INSTALLATION

Run setup.py with the "install" command, e.g.:

    python setup.py install

This library has been tested on Python 2.7 and Python 3.2.


USAGE

Import the tmx library in your project file.  You can then save and
load TMX files with the tmx.TileMap class.

See the docstrings for detailed information.  Access them with the help
function, e.g. ``help(tmx)``.
